  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Help save a school for 300 students in Nepal</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Ek Pahila&apos;s objective is to help save a school building and a bathroom for 300 students in Nepal from being washed away by the monsoon rains. These buildings are already under threat due to the heavy erosion that has been occurring every year. We will also paint the school buildings so that classrooms are waterproof. This will create a better learning environment for the students. Moreover, we also plan to establish a proper workplace for the principal and teachers at Devisthan Primary School.</narrative>
  </description>
